OL,5, The price of petrol surged by nearly 5p
OL,6, a litre in the week that included the  
OL,7, bank holiday break, the RAC says, and  
OL,8, could soon hit 180p a litre.           
OL,10,FThe motoring body said the average cost
OL,11,Fof a litre of petrol had hit a         
OL,12,F"frightening" 177.88p by Sunday.       
OL,14,FOil prices remain high due to the war  
OL,15,Fin Ukraine and sanctions to reduce     
OL,16,FEurope's dependence on Russia.         
OL,18,FIn March, the government cut fuel duty 
OL,19,Fby 5p a litre for a year, but the RAC  
OL,20,Fcalled for more help for motorists.    
